        <updateDate>2019-09-03T16:22:03Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Ban Conflicted Trading Act</b></p> <p>This bill prohibits a Member of Congress or certain congressional officers or employees from (1) purchasing or selling specified investments, (2) entering into a transaction that creates a net short position in a security, and (3) serving as an officer or member of any board of any for-profit entity.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
